<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 16:10:42 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>哈马斯人质的父亲说：“如果内塔尼亚胡想要达成协议，这次采访就不会进行”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/if-netanyahu-wanted-a-deal-this-interview-wouldnt-have-taken-place/00000191-5b72-d101-a7fd-7bffd9ed0000</link><description>伊齐克·霍恩（Itzik Horn）花了数周时间并承受巨大压力才得知他的两个儿子亚伊尔（Yair）和埃坦（Eitan）被关押在加沙。这位阿根廷出生的父亲猛烈抨击那些“背着人质”为加沙带来秩序的人，并建议内塔尼亚胡派他的儿子亚伊尔前往加沙，带回霍恩的儿子亚伊尔</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 14:59:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/if-netanyahu-wanted-a-deal-this-interview-wouldnt-have-taken-place/00000191-5b72-d101-a7fd-7bffd9ed0000</guid></item><item><title>10月7日已经足够令人震惊了。以色列人为何要粉饰这场悲剧？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-08-16/ty-article-opinion/.premium/october-7-was-shocking-enough-why-should-israelis-embellish-the-tragedy/00000191-5a8b-d316-a9f1-decb1be60000</link><description></description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 14:27:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-08-16/ty-article-opinion/.premium/october-7-was-shocking-enough-why-should-israelis-embellish-the-tragedy/00000191-5a8b-d316-a9f1-decb1be60000</guid></item><item><title>美国殖民地酒店希望成为一座理智的岛屿。随后加沙战争爆发</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/travel/2024-08-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-american-colony-hotel-hoped-to-be-an-island-of-sanity-then-the-war-broke-out/00000191-5b57-d761-afd9-7f576bf10000</link><description>该酒店是耶路撒冷的标志性建筑，但由于入住率直线下降，其生存在其 100 年历史中首次面临危险</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 13:46:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/travel/2024-08-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-american-colony-hotel-hoped-to-be-an-island-of-sanity-then-the-war-broke-out/00000191-5b57-d761-afd9-7f576bf10000</guid></item><item><title>总理办公室数据显示，截至 10 月 7 日，内塔尼亚胡已出国六次，花费超过 600 万美元</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/until-oct-7-netanyahu-flew-abroad-six-times-at-cost-of-over-6-million-pmo-data-shows/00000191-5afa-d101-a7fd-7aff08c70000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡在巴黎、罗马和柏林的停留各持续三天，其中巴黎是最昂贵的，花费了纳税人100万美元。罗马的旅行费用约为 50 万美元，柏林为 302,000 美元</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 12:52:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/until-oct-7-netanyahu-flew-abroad-six-times-at-cost-of-over-6-million-pmo-data-shows/00000191-5afa-d101-a7fd-7aff08c70000</guid></item><item><title>世界必须做出决定：执行加沙授权还是让中东的流血事件继续下去</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/the-world-must-decide-implement-gaza-mandate-or-let-the-bloodshed-in-the-region-continue/00000191-5a0a-d753-a395-dbeba59f0000</link><description>巴勒斯坦权力机构没有能力治理加沙，以色列唯一有战后计划的是那些支持吞并的人。虽然让加沙重返托管时代听起来像是另一次殖民主义干预的开始，但事实上，国际机构已经在管理加沙地带</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 09:04:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/the-world-must-decide-implement-gaza-mandate-or-let-the-bloodshed-in-the-region-continue/00000191-5a0a-d753-a395-dbeba59f0000</guid></item><item><title>犹太定居者袭击西岸村庄；巴勒斯坦人死亡，一人重伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-vows-to-prosecute-israeli-settlers-after-deadly-riots-in-west-bank-village/00000191-57a6-dacb-a7bf-f7ae83f10000</link><description>周四晚上，数十名犹太定居者突然袭击吉特，造成至少一人死亡；亚伊尔·戈兰：“定居者是一个暴力团体，得到政府的大力支持”</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 07:53:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-vows-to-prosecute-israeli-settlers-after-deadly-riots-in-west-bank-village/00000191-57a6-dacb-a7bf-f7ae83f10000</guid></item><item><title>加沙停火、人质谈判将于周五继续；卡塔尔总理向伊朗通报了谈判进展情况</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/gaza-cease-fire-hostage-talks-to-continue-friday-qatari-pm-updated-iran-on-progress/00000191-59a8-db91-a7dd-7fa8abb50000</link><description>一位消息人士告诉《国土报》，“双方希望在未来 24 小时内看到进展”。伊朗还收到了谈判的最新情况，表明伊朗间接参与了谈判，以及美国、卡塔尔和埃及为防止伊朗和真主党升级而做出的努力</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 06:02:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/gaza-cease-fire-hostage-talks-to-continue-friday-qatari-pm-updated-iran-on-progress/00000191-59a8-db91-a7dd-7fa8abb50000</guid></item><item><title>“现在，在以色列，人们已经撤离家园。但我们从一个星球搬到了另一个星球”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/now-many-israelis-have-evacuated-their-homes-but-we-moved-from-one-planet-to-another/00000191-5929-d316-a9f1-dde9fd4c0000</link><description>她经历过失落、拒绝和局外人的痛苦，但从未离开过舞台。 94 岁高龄的以色列剧院第一夫人 Lea Koenig 谈论如何才能过上长久而有意义的生活</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 04:19:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/now-many-israelis-have-evacuated-their-homes-but-we-moved-from-one-planet-to-another/00000191-5929-d316-a9f1-dde9fd4c0000</guid></item><item><title>“当我从我的与生俱来的权利之旅回到家时，我将开始去犹太教堂”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-08-16/ty-article/.highlight/when-i-get-back-home-from-my-birthright-trip-ill-start-going-to-synagogue/00000191-592a-d316-a9f1-ddeab4d10000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：一位从小信奉天主教长大的美国人在以色列之行中学到了很多东西，而一位以色列人则因为“神灵把他送到那里”而进入萨满教</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 03:40:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-08-16/ty-article/.highlight/when-i-get-back-home-from-my-birthright-trip-ill-start-going-to-synagogue/00000191-592a-d316-a9f1-ddeab4d10000</guid></item><item><title>美国人正在发放胡萝卜，但内塔尼亚胡更担心国内的大棒