/netanyahu-israeli-leaders-condemn-deadly-settler-violence-idf-shin-bet-to-investigate/00000191-5905-d316-a9f1-ddc52c520000</link><description>报道：真主党不会在卡塔尔谈判期间对以色列发动袭击，报复“并不紧急” ■ 蒙面定居者袭击约旦河西岸村庄后，巴勒斯坦人被杀；美国谴责袭击事件 ■ 停火、释放人质谈判在卡塔尔继续进行 ■ 法国、英国外长将在耶路撒冷会见以色列外长</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 02:42:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article-live/.premium/netanyahu-israeli-leaders-condemn-deadly-settler-violence-idf-shin-bet-to-investigate/00000191-5905-d316-a9f1-ddc52c520000</guid></item><item><title>特朗普、哈里斯在民主党大会前竞选活动中犹太人投票为零</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/trump-harris-campaigns-zero-in-on-jewish-vote-ahead-of-democratic-convention/00000191-58ce-db91-a7dd-7fce1ee40000</link><description>在这次选举中，以色列和反犹太主义可能比以往任何一场选举都更受关注，两个阵营都利用明星影响力、巨额捐助者和网络来争取犹太社区的支持</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 02:14:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/trump-harris-campaigns-zero-in-on-jewish-vote-ahead-of-democratic-convention/00000191-58ce-db91-a7dd-7fce1ee40000</guid></item><item><title>巴克莱银行撤销退出下一次政府债券拍卖的决定，以色列松了一口气</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/israel-relieved-as-barclays-reverses-decision-to-withdraw-from-next-govt-bond-auction/00000191-581c-dacb-a7bf-fb3cd3fe0000</link><description>以色列总会计师欢迎英国银行“抵制反犹太主义和反以色列压力，特别是 BDS 运动推动的压力”的决定</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 22:42:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/israel-relieved-as-barclays-reverses-decision-to-withdraw-from-next-govt-bond-auction/00000191-581c-dacb-a7bf-fb3cd3fe0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列退休警察：10月7日是“最基本的失败”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/retired-israeli-cop-only-900-officers-sent-to-south-during-october-7-attack/00000191-573c-d203-abb5-5f3cd1830000</link><description>退役少将阿姆农·阿尔卡莱 (Amnon Alkalay) 表示，“这是一次非常严重、灾难性的管理事件”，他援引了仅向南方派遣 900 名警察的决定，而“人们却连续几个小时遭到屠杀”</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 19:47:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/retired-israeli-cop-only-900-officers-sent-to-south-during-october-7-attack/00000191-573c-d203-abb5-5f3cd1830000</guid></item><item><title>抗议者走上特拉维夫街头，呼吁在卡塔尔峰会期间达成人质协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/protesters-take-to-streets-of-tel-aviv-call-for-hostage-deal-amid-qatar-summit/00000191-5713-d79a-a3f5-dfd30adc0000</link><description>一名人质亲属表示，“人质事件是以色列国历史上最大的安全、社会、道德和宗教失败的证据”，示威者敦促以色列谈判代表不要在没有达成协议的情况下从卡塔尔返回</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 19:06:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/protesters-take-to-streets-of-tel-aviv-call-for-hostage-deal-amid-qatar-summit/00000191-5713-d79a-a3f5-dfd30adc0000</guid></item><item><title>中东局势岌岌可危，除了与伊朗全面战争之外，以色列左翼还有其他选择</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/on-the-israeli-left-there-is-still-an-alternative-to-all-out-war-with-iran/00000191-562b-d61e-a7b1-f7ff54d10000</link><description>左翼在安全问题上始终处于守势。但现在，在等待伊朗袭击以色列的漫长而可怕的等待中，除了内塔尼亚胡的灾难性政策之外，还有一个替代方案：对一个全副武装、有充分理由进行报复的死敌采取自由、进步的态度</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 18:50:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/on-the-israeli-left-there-is-still-an-alternative-to-all-out-war-with-iran/00000191-562b-d61e-a7b1-f7ff54d10000</guid></item><item><title>《早安乔》透露：内塔尼亚胡终于失去了亲以色列的美国人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-15/ty-article/.highlight/at-long-last-netanyahu-is-losing-pro-israel-americans/00000191-5674-d887-adbd-77f509d30000</link><description>乔·斯卡伯勒和退役美国海军上将詹姆斯·斯塔夫里迪斯在“早安乔”节目中的对话反映了许多美国人都知道的事情：内塔尼亚胡是一位腐败的政客，不惜一切代价紧握权力</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 18:16:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-15/ty-article/.highlight/at-long-last-netanyahu-is-losing-pro-israel-americans/00000191-5674-d887-adbd-77f509d30000</guid></item><item><title>斯塔默总理当选后，以色列罕见延长驻英国大使任期</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/in-rare-move-israel-to-extend-term-of-ambassador-to-u-k-following-election-of-pm-starmer/00000191-56d2-d79a-a3f5-ded20fd30000</link><description>以色列外交部正在寻求延长齐皮·霍托夫利 (Tzipi Hotovley) 以色列驻英国大使的任期，理由是她拥有“广泛的关系网络”以及推进以色列“战略利益”的能力</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 16:52:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/in-rare-move-israel-to-extend-term-of-ambassador-to-u-k-following-election-of-pm-starmer/00000191-56d2-d79a-a3f5-ded20fd30000</guid></item></channel></rss>